#input data
inputdata.10x <- Read10X_h5("pbmc_granulocyte_sorted_10k_filtered_feature_bc_matrix.h5")
## Genome matrix has multiple modalities, returning a list of matrices for this genome
rna_counts <- inputdata.10x$`Gene Expression`
atac_counts <- inputdata.10x$Peaks
cell_type = readRDS('cell_type.RDS')

#RNA modality
pbmc_rna <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = rna_counts[,rownames(cell_type)],assay = 'RNA')
pbmc_rna = NormalizeData(object = pbmc_rna,scale.factor = 10^6)
## Normalizing layer: counts
pbmc_rna = FindVariableFeatures(pbmc_rna,nfeatures = 3000)
## Finding variable features for layer counts
pbmc_rna = ScaleData(pbmc_rna)
## Centering and scaling data matrix
var_gene = VariableFeatures(pbmc_rna)
pbmc_rna <- RunPCA(pbmc_rna)

#ATAC modality
annotations <- GetGRangesFromEnsDb(ensdb = EnsDb.Hsapiens.v86)
seqlevels(annotations) <- paste0('chr', seqlevels(annotations))
genome(annotations) <- "hg38"
pbmc.atac = CreateChromatinAssay(counts = atac_counts[,rownames(cell_type)],sep = c(":", "-"),annotation = annotations,
                                 fragments = 'pbmc_granulocyte_sorted_10k_atac_fragments.tsv.gz')
## Computing hash
pbmc.atac = CreateSeuratObject(counts = pbmc.atac,assay = 'ATAC')

gas = GeneActivity(object = pbmc.atac,features = var_gene) #calculating gene activity score
## Extracting gene coordinates
## Extracting reads overlapping genomic regions
pbmc.atac <- RunTFIDF(pbmc.atac)
## Performing TF-IDF normalization
pbmc.atac <- FindTopFeatures(pbmc.atac, min.cutoff = 'q0')
pbmc.atac <- RunSVD(pbmc.atac)
## Running SVD
## Scaling cell embeddings
pbmc.atac <- RunUMAP(pbmc.atac, reduction = "lsi", dims = 2:30, reduction.name = "umap.atac", reduction.key = "atacUMAP_")

rna_seurat = pbmc_rna
atac_seurat = pbmc.atac
ATAC_expression = gas

atac_seurat[["ACTIVITY"]] = CreateAssayObject(counts = ATAC_expression)
DefaultAssay(atac_seurat) <- "ACTIVITY"
atac_seurat <- NormalizeData(atac_seurat)
atac_seurat <- ScaleData(atac_seurat, features = rownames(atac_seurat))
## Centering and scaling data matrix
var_gene = rownames(ATAC_expression)

# Identify anchors
transfer.anchors <- FindTransferAnchors(reference = rna_seurat, query = atac_seurat, features =  var_gene,
                                        reference.assay = "RNA", query.assay = "ACTIVITY", reduction = "cca")
## Running CCA
## Merging objects
## Finding neighborhoods
## Finding anchors
##  Found 24502 anchors
refdata = (rna_seurat@assays$RNA$data)[var_gene,]
imputation <- TransferData(anchorset = transfer.anchors, refdata = refdata,weight.reduction = atac_seurat[["lsi"]],dims = 2:50)
## Finding integration vectors
## Finding integration vector weights
## Transfering 1908 features onto reference data
#transfer label
cell_label = cell_type[colnames(rna_seurat),]
predicted_label <- TransferData(anchorset = transfer.anchors, refdata = cell_label,weight.reduction = atac_seurat[["lsi"]],dims = 2:50)
## Finding integration vectors
## Finding integration vector weights
## Predicting cell labels
#Co-embedding
rna_data = rna_seurat@assays$RNA$data[var_gene,]
atac_data = imputation@data[rownames(rna_data),]
colnames(atac_data) = paste0(colnames(atac_data),'_atac')
coembed_data <- cbind(rna_data,atac_data)
coembed = CreateSeuratObject(coembed_data)
coembed$modality = c(rep('RNA',ncol(rna_data)),rep('ATAC',ncol(rna_data)))
coembed$cell_type = c(cell_label,predicted_label$predicted.id)
coembed = NormalizeData(coembed)
## Normalizing layer: counts
coembed@assays$RNA$data = coembed_data
coembed <- ScaleData(coembed, features = var_gene, do.scale = FALSE)
## Centering data matrix
coembed <- RunPCA(coembed, features = var_gene, verbose = FALSE)
coembed <- RunUMAP(coembed,dims = 1:50)

#Evaluation
metric = function(label,embed){

  writeLines(gsub(" ","_",paste(cell_type[,1],collapse = ',')), "tmp_file/true_label.txt")
  writeLines(gsub(" ","_",paste(label[rownames(cell_type),1],collapse = ',')), "tmp_file/pred_label.txt")
  write.csv(embed, "tmp_file/tmp_cord.csv", row.names = FALSE, quote = FALSE)
  command <- sprintf("/dssg/home/acct-clswt/clswt-chaodeng/miniconda3/bin/python ~/metric.py")
  metric = capture.output(system(command,intern = TRUE))
  return(metric)
}
metric_result = metric(label = predicted_label,embed = coembed@reductions$pca@cell.embeddings)
print(metric_result)
